00:23:03.292 --> 00:23:05.072
people that gave us funding to do this

404
00:23:06.072 --> 00:23:09.432
research. And I'm going to take questions, if any.

405
00:23:09.472 --> 00:23:11.692
Thank you very much.

406
00:23:15.832 --> 00:23:16.632
Nice work. So,

